8ae3467ba","tid":222460,"uid":82481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"可以試下落街做個運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人覺得跑步幾減壓<br />\n反而之前壓力大同亂諗野果陣，訓愈多愈頹喪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c72e58607d53939a56b98ddf2e0f34a51271145","tid":222460,"uid":96927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去睇下海 出去行下會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前有聽海嘅習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過而家太忙 同埋好多人流<br />\n<br />\n所以冇乜心情同時間去聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽海真係好舒服 匿埋眼感受下d海風同聲 <br />\n<br />\n果種感覺好似咩都唔洗理 自己去咗一個好安靜好和諧嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d463715883d0a5daf346f5c5719fb74de953a2","tid":222460,"uid":96927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喊下都幾減壓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好驚喊 因為一喊自己就會越諗越負面<br />\n<br />\n所以自己好少喊<br />\n<br />\n不過人人而異嘅"},{"pid":"1490fdfb491254359431b075bf4e262cb896b9d3","tid":222460,"uid":96927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得巴打你都好勁架啦 又自己出黎住 又番工又讀書 大多野逼埋黎 我都會頂唔住 喊下搵下朋友都係唔錯既減壓方法 頂住啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過可惜我係個小毒毒<br />\n<br />\n冇乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21844f79242957c56c8a30674daccfd6b3b1ded6","tid":222460,"uid":91399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"其實喊係好正常嘅抒發情緒途徑<br />\n我有時都會開個花灑伴奏默默飲泣<br />\n<br />\n過埋呢兩個禮拜又sem break喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"